{"type":"message","id":"153a7c18","parentId":"c5e27034","timestamp":"2026-02-18T01:58:22.428Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"  yfinance is not installable in the externally-managed environment. Let me use a free stock API instead, or we can skip stocks. Let me try fetching stock data from a free API like Yahoo Finance via web scraping or another API endpoint.\n\nActually, let me just proceed with the data I have (Bitcoin and GitHub repos) and mention that stock data is currently unavailable. Or I could try using a free stock quote API.\n\nLet me try another approach - I can use an alternative free stock price API or just proceed without stocks for now. Given the time, let me send what I have with a note about stocks, or I could try one more approach - using curl to fetch from Yahoo Finance unofficial API.\n\nActually, let me just send the message with Bitcoin and GitHub data, and note that stock fetching failed. This is a \"daily ping\" cron job, so partial data is better than","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":" Let me try an alternative for"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"  functions.exec:4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport urllib.request\nimport urllib.parse\nimport json\n\n# Try to fetch from Yahoo Finance via their chart API (no auth needed for basic quotes)\ntickers = ['NVDA', 'MSFT', 'GOOGL', 'INTC', 'META', 'AMD']\nresults = {}\n\nfor t in tickers:\n    try:\n        url = f'https://query1.finance.yahoo.com/v8/finance/chart/{t}?range=1d&interval=1d'\n        req = urllib.request.Request(url, headers={'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0'})\n        with urllib.request.urlopen(req, timeout=10) as response:\n            data = json.loads(response.read())\n            meta = data['chart']['result'][0]['meta']\n            price = meta.get('regularMarketPrice', 'N/A')\n            prev = meta.get('previousClose', 'N/A')\n            if price != 'N/A' and prev != 'N/A':\n                change_pct = round(((price - prev) / prev) * 100, 2)\n            else:\n                change_pct = 'N/A'\n            results[t] = {'price': round(price, 2) if price != 'N/A' else 'N/A', 'change_pct': change_pct}\n    except Exception as e:\n        results[t] = {'price': 'N/A', 'change_pct': 'N/A'}\n\nprint(json.dumps(results))\n\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"moonshotai/kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":20490,"output":545,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21035,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771379796934}}
